column5: BRZU With PBR Oil price down how do you manage to have POSITIVE number I bet its your interest rate

PBR Update on Social Security Reforms On Sunday they delayed the presentation to tomorrow which will be at 830 EST As of now there are no further delays and is with the hard deadline of June 15th which anything beyond that deadline would risk approval in the House by midJuly recess Increasing speculation that the reform package will be more robust that thought a couple of weeks ago 800B in savings seems to be what the market is pricing in with high probabilities So anything at that level or more would be read positively by the markets clearly the more the better
